Misty Aura
Discworld ritual help
Misty Aura

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Misty Aura - Summons a shield to protect your target.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This is a ritual used by those who worship Pishe, which summons a
shield of mist, given holy strength, to protect them.  The 
effectiveness of the shield will depend on your skill in working
defensive rituals, and the ritual requires a holy symbol to perform.
.EP
